Over the weekend, we had the pleasure of sitting down with Ms. @ElizabethWoods for an interview at @KarlJhair’s First Annual Beauty Brunch! As a management and business mogul, Ms. Woods is a true embodiment of beauty and girl power! 

It is so important for us as women to continue to build ourselves and each other up and raise intelligent, powerful young ladies of the future! With all of the gems she dropped, I can’t think of a better way to have spent the #BETawards weekend!

Subscribe to our YouTube channel via the #linkinbio to catch up on past episodes and turn your notifications on before the full interview drops on Monday, July 3!
